FBIS3-40047 "drweu038_p_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-038 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Feb 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS New Finance, Deputy Ministers Appointed NC2402142394 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 1230 GMT 24 Feb 94 NC2402142394 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Language: Greek Article Type:BFN [Text] Deputy Finance Minister Alexandros Papadhopoulos and Nikolaos Kiriazidhis, an expert at the Finance Ministry, will be sworn in as finance minister and deputy finance minister respectively. The swearing-in ceremony will be held at noon tomorrow before President Konstandinos Karamanlis and Prime Minister Andreas Papandreou. Government spokesman Evangelos Venizelos said that the changes in the Finance Ministry were made following consultations between Prime Minister Andreas Papandreou and National Economy Minister Yeoryios Yennimatas.
